import React from "react"
import "./Devui.css"
import { Row, Col } from "react-bootstrap"
import Navigation from "./Navigation"

const Devui = () => {

    return (
        <>
            <Row>
                <Navigation />
            </Row>
            <Row className="listingpgtopbg mt-4">
                <Col className="justify_All_center">

                    Project means applying your technical knowledge in shaping a real-life object.

                </Col>
            </Row>
            
        </>
    )
}

export default Devui
